y 62 pet even fully buffed can't tank the loroks in PoS for more than 10 seconds).<br>
<br>
Personally I have a friend wizard who i partner with. Sometimes I partner with a druid. Soloing is great for gaining those AA as each kill (from the typhoon loroks) gives you about 4-5% AA xp per kill which is pretty sweet.<br>
